data.title: Kelly Mantle
data.meta_description: Kelly Leroy Mantle is an American actor, singer-songwriter, comedian, musician, drag queen, and reality television personality. Mantle appeared as a contestant on the sixth season of the reality TV show RuPaul's Drag Race.
